message.content:
Here is an example of a shark hunting landing page without the HTML, HEAD, BODY, and SCRIPT tags as requested. The HTML code is wrapped between the `---starthtml---` and `---endhtml---` tags, the CSS code is wrapped between the `---startcss---` and `---endcss---` tags, and the JavaScript code is wrapped between the `---startjs---` and `---endjs---` tags.

---starthtml---
<div class="header">
  <h1>Shark Hunting Adventures</h1>
  <nav>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Gallery</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
</div>

<main>
  <section class="banner">
    <h2>Experience the Thrill of Shark Hunting</h2>
    <p>Get up close and personal with some of the most fascinating creatures in the ocean.</p>
    <a href="#" class="cta-button">Book Your Adventure</a>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="feature">
      <img src="shark-fin.png" alt="Shark Fin">
      <h3>Explore the Deep</h3>
      <p>Discover the hidden wonders of the ocean and the amazing creatures that call it home.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature">
      <img src="shark-cage.png" alt="Shark Cage">
      <h3>Safe and Secure</h3>
      <p>Experience the thrill of shark hunting in a safe and controlled environment.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature">
      <img src="shark-trophy.png" alt="Shark Trophy">
      <h3>Take Home a Trophy</h3>
      <p>Show off your hunting prowess with a trophy from your adventure.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="testimonial">
    <blockquote>"Shark hunting with these guys was an incredible experience. They know how to make you feel safe while still getting your adrenaline pumping. I would definitely recommend them to anyone looking for an adventure."</blockquote>
    <cite>John D.</cite>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  <div class="footer-nav">
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Gallery</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-social">
    <a href="#"><img src="facebook.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
    <a href="#"><img src="twitter.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
    <a href="#"><img src="instagram.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-info">
    <p>Shark Hunting Adventures &copy; 2021</p>
  </div>
</footer>
---endhtml---

---startcss---
body {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}

.header {
  background-color: #333;
  color: #fff;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 1rem;
}

.header h1 {
  font-size: 2rem;
  margin: 0;
}

.header nav ul {
  list-style: none;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

.header nav li {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-right: 1rem;
}

.header nav a {
  color: #fff;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.banner {
  background-image: url('shark-banner.jpg');
  background-size: cover;
  height: 500px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
}

.banner h2 {
  font-size: 3rem;
  color: #fff;
  margin: 0;
}

.banner p {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  color: #fff;
  margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
}

.cta-button {
  background-color: #f1c40f;
  color: #333;
  padding: 1rem 2rem;
  border-radius: 2rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.features {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 2rem;
}

.feature {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  margin-right: 1rem;
}

.feature img {
  width: 150px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.feature h3 {
  font-size: 2rem;
  margin: 0;
}

.feature p {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.testimonial {
  background-color: #333;
  color: #fff;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 2rem;
}

.testimonial blockquote {
  font-size: 2rem;
  margin: 0;
}

.testimonial cite {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
}

.footer {
  background-color: #333;
  color: #fff;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  padding-top: 2rem;
  padding-bottom: 2rem;
}

.footer-nav ul {
  list-style: none;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.footer-nav li {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-right: 1rem;
}

.footer-nav a {
  color: #fff;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.footer-social {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.footer-social img {
  width: 30px;
  margin-right: 1rem;
}

.footer-info {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}
---endcss---

